00:52:26,791 --> 00:52:27,823
And?

506
00:52:29,127 --> 00:52:30,456
And?

507
00:52:33,341 --> 00:52:34,336
Don't you see?

508
00:52:34,592 --> 00:52:37,843
l see a description that fits
a number of juvenile murders.

509
00:52:38,096 --> 00:52:41,382
