This big, black car?

523
00:53:26,861 --> 00:53:28,106
This is not a truck.

524
00:53:28,362 --> 00:53:31,566
This is not a maroon truck
like Wadenah drove.

525
00:53:31,825 --> 00:53:34,696
This is a big, black station wagon.

526
00:53:34,953 --> 00:53:37,871
And these right here,
according to an interview l had. . .

527
00:53:38,124 --> 00:53:42,039
. . .with a girl named Beck--
Betsy Fiske. . .

528
00:53:42,295 --> 00:53:44,787
