-Okay. Whoa! Hold it.

529
00:53:45,048 --> 00:53:47,374
Porcupines and giants and--

530
00:53:47,635 --> 00:53:50,256
You got to get ahold
of yourself, Jerry.

531
00:53:50,513 --> 00:53:52,589
The case is closed.

532
00:53:54,559 --> 00:53:56,469
l made a promise.

533
00:53:57,396 --> 00:54:01,097
l made a promise to find. . .

534
00:54:02,652 --> 00:54:04,977
. . .Ginny Larsen's murderer.

535
00:54:05,697 --> 00:54:07,405
l intend to keep it.

536
00:54:21,132 --> 00:54:23,089
Listen, Jerry.

537
00:54:25,595 --> 00:54:28,596
You gotta start getting on
with your life, you know?

538
00:54:30,225 --> 00:54:34,271
l mean, sometimes when you
go through big changes. . .

539
00:54:34,522 --> 00:54:36,396
. . .and retirement's one of them. . .

540
00:54:36,649 --> 00:54:39,520
. . .it can cause a lot of added stress.

541
00:54:40,737 --> 00:54:42,980
Sometimes it's a good idea just to. . .

542
00:54:43,658 --> 00:54:46,030
. . .talk to someone.
You know, someone. . .

543
00:54:46,995 --> 00:54:48,074
. . .professional.

544
00:54:48,788 --> 00:54:50,532
l made a promise, Eric.

545
00:54:50,791 --> 00:54:53,876
You're old enough to remember
when that meant something.

546
00:55:02,846 --> 00:55:04,590
Get a life.

547
00:55:53,947 --> 00:55:56,783
Jerry, got your fresh towels here!

548
00:55:57,534 --> 00:55:59,408
Most don't need them every day.

549
00:55:59,662 --> 00:56:03,743
Please don't get them so dirty
they're not to be white again.

550
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:07,500
Here's your nice little sunroom.
You can smoke in here.

551
00:56:07,755 --> 00:56:11,089
This is the living room area.
No partying, please, no.

552
00:56:11,342 --> 00:56:14,130
Kitchen, of course.
All the amenities of home.

553
00:56:14,387 --> 00:56:18,255
Bedroom. We just got a new mattress,
so it should be really comfy.

554
00:56:18,517 --> 00:56:21,637
And oh, yeah, trash goes
in the covered dumpster.

555
00:56:21,896 --> 00:56:26,891
Fish guts you gotta wrap and place in
the pail next to the cleaning station.

